{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were preparing already-- they were called the Bricha-- the Zionist organization-- Bricha.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were doing a very efficient job to organize people and young people, you know, to go to Israel before it was Israel, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we had the chance to go with, with them to, to leave Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, we stayed in Liegnitz a short time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were working the kibbutz, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a job that I worked, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is how we, everybody went to work and brought a check, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is how, you know, money to buy food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the kibbutz liquidated, we all went across the border to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Czechoslovakia, we were not supposed to say that we are from Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we had to say that we are Greeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going home to Greek-- to Greece.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the Russians supposed to ask us questions, we don't know Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't know Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are Greeks, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we came to Austria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We came to Austria, in [NON-ENGLISH], but my future wife's parents, she went-- they went to in different kibbutz for grown-up people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were for youngsters, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And her brother was in the children's kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when we left Poland, they went-- no, we went before-- no, the parents went before us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went secondary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the boy went with another kibbutz, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, we took-- they took us to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ebensee was a, a, a concentration camp, was like Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had ovens and gas chambers, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were killing Jews in a wholesale way, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
